cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use claude-rank in research, content, or production work, please cite it as below."
title: "claude-rank: AI Readiness and Search Visibility scanner for Claude Code"
abstract: "Claude Code plugin that tells you why your site won't get cited by AI — and fixes the discoverability files automatically. 10 scanners, 170+ rules covering SEO (Google, Bing), GEO (Generative Engine Optimization — Perplexity, ChatGPT, Gemini), and AEO (Answer Engine Optimization — featured snippets, voice search). Auto-fix for robots.txt, sitemap.xml, llms.txt, and JSON-LD."
